Fy_shipment

Created by Unstoppable
Also made glasstrap_final

This is a fun small map which supports up to 40 players.

Terrorists can go in to a secert container if they know
the key code.

Counter-Terrorists should rush the container and shoot
at it like crazy killing any Terrorists inside.


Tip:
======
The key code to get in the secret container is hiddin
somewhere in the map.
